import warnings
warnings.filterwarnings('ignore')
import os

from matplotlib import pyplot as plt
plt.rcParams['figure.figsize'] = 12, 10
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import numpy as np
from sklearn.model_selection import TimeSeriesSplit  
from sklearn.model_selection import cross_val_score
from sklearn.linear_model import LinearRegression, Lasso, Ridge
import xgboost as xgb
from sklearn.svm import SVR
from sklearn.preprocessing import StandardScaler
from sklearn.ensemble import RandomForestRegressor
import preprocess, process

# Columns: 'Date','open','high','low','close','volume','lag_1','lag_2','lag_3','lag_4','lag_5','lag_10',
# 'lag_21','lag_42','lag_63','return_1d','return_2d','return_3d','return_4d','return_5d','return_10d',
# 'return_21d','return_42d','return_63d','rsi','bb_high','bb_low','atr','macd','sma_10','sma_20','sma_50',
# 'ema_10','ema_20','ema_50','weekday_0','weekday_1','weekday_2','weekday_3','weekday_4','month_1',
# 'month_2','month_3','month_4','month_5','month_6','month_7','month_8','month_9','month_10','month_11',
# 'month_12','target_close','target_return_1d','target_class'

# company = ticker value 'AAPL', 'MSFT', 'GOOG', 'AMZN', 'NVDA', 'META', 'TSLA', 'BRK-B', 'LLY', 'V'
COMPANY = 'GOOG'  
STRATEGY = 'target_close_all_lags'
TARGET = 'target_close'    
FEATURES = ['close','lag_1','lag_2','lag_3','lag_4','lag_5','lag_10','lag_21','lag_42','lag_63']

INPUT_FILE = f'{COMPANY}//data//{COMPANY}_data.csv'
df = preprocess.read_data(INPUT_FILE, display=True)

X, y = preprocess.preprocess_data(df, TARGET, FEATURES, True)

test_len = 260
train_end_idx = -test_len
test_start_idx = -test_len
least_train_len = 260 # train on at least year of observations

X_train, y_train, X_test, y_test = preprocess.split_data(X, y,train_end_idx, test_start_idx, True)

sc = StandardScaler()
X_train_sc = sc.fit_transform(X_train)
X_test_sc = sc.transform(X_test)

print(f'X TRAIN SCALED :: {X_train_sc}')

nr_splits = process.calculate_split_folds(X_train_sc, least_train_len, test_len)

tscv = TimeSeriesSplit(n_splits=nr_splits, test_size=test_len)

preprocess.print_tscv(df, tscv, X_train_sc)

SCORER = 'explained_variance'
SCORE_METRICS = ['explained_variance','r2', 'neg_mean_absolute_error', 'neg_mean_squared_error', 'neg_median_absolute_error']

# Linear Regression
lr = LinearRegression()
lr_param_grid = {}
lr = process.get_gs_model_per_alg(lr, tscv, lr_param_grid, SCORER, X_train_sc, y_train)

# Lasso, Ridge
lasso = Lasso()
alpha_param_grid = {
 'alpha': [0.0001, 0.001,0.01, 0.1, 1, 10]
 }

lasso = Lasso()
lasso = process.get_gs_model_per_alg(lasso, tscv, alpha_param_grid, SCORER, X_train_sc, y_train)

ridge = Ridge()
ridge = process.get_gs_model_per_alg(ridge, tscv, alpha_param_grid, SCORER, X_train_sc, y_train)


# RandomForestRegressor
rand_for = RandomForestRegressor()
rand_for_param_grid = {'n_estimators': [20, 50, 100],'max_features': [1.0, 'sqrt', 'log2'],'max_depth' : [3, 5, 7, 9, 11, 13, 15]}
rand_for = process.get_gs_model_per_alg(rand_for, tscv, rand_for_param_grid, SCORER, X_train_sc, y_train)

# XGBoost
xgbr = xgb.XGBRegressor()
xgb_param_grid = {'max_depth': [3, 5, 7, 9, 11, 13, 15], 'learning_rate': [0.1, 0.2, 0.3]}
xgboost = process.get_gs_model_per_alg(xgbr, tscv, xgb_param_grid, SCORER, X_train_sc, y_train)

#SVR
svr = SVR()
svr_param_grid = {'kernel' : ['linear', 'rbf'],'C' : [1, 10],'gamma' : ['scale']}
svr = process.get_gs_model_per_alg(svr, tscv, svr_param_grid, SCORER, X_train, y_train)

# Save models
models=[]
models.append(('LR', lr))
models.append(('Lasso', lasso))
models.append(('Ridge', ridge))
models.append(('RandomForest', rand_for))
models.append(('XGB', xgboost))
#models.append(('SVR', svr))
  
saved_models_files = process.save_fitted_models(models, COMPANY, SCORER, test_len, STRATEGY)
print(saved_models_files)

# Choose best models
best_models=[]
best_models.append(('LR', lr.best_estimator_))
best_models.append(('Lasso', lasso.best_estimator_))
best_models.append(('Ridge', ridge.best_estimator_))
best_models.append(('RandomForest', rand_for.best_estimator_))
best_models.append(('XGB', xgboost.best_estimator_))
best_models.append(('SVR', svr.best_estimator_))

def evaluate(best_models, test_len, tscv, x_train, y_train):
    df_cv_results = pd.DataFrame()
    df_feat_imp = pd.DataFrame()
    for score in SCORE_METRICS:
        print(f'SCORE :: {score}') 
        results = []
        names = [] 
        for name, best_model in best_models:
            names.append(name)
            cv_results = cross_val_score(best_model, x_train, y_train, cv=tscv, scoring=score)
            print('%s: %f %f (%f)' % (name, cv_results.mean(), np.median(cv_results), cv_results.std()))
            # Appending to file
            #result_output = f'{name} {score}:mean={cv_results.mean()} median={np.median(cv_results)} std={cv_results.std()}\n'
            cv_result_series = pd.Series({'strategy': STRATEGY, 'test_len': test_len, 'model': name, 'metric': score, 'mean': cv_results.mean(),'median': np.median(cv_results),'std' :cv_results.std()})
            df_cv_results = pd.concat([df_cv_results, cv_result_series.to_frame().T], ignore_index=True)
            #with open(f"{test_len}_cv_results.txt", 'a') as file:
            #    file.write(result_output)
            results.append(cv_results)
            print(f"NAME {name}")

            if (("Lasso" in name or "Ridge" in name or "LR" in name or "SVR" in name) and len(best_model.coef_)==1):
                imp = best_model.coef_[0]
            if (("Lasso" in name or "Ridge" in name or "LR" in name or "SVR" in name) and len(best_model.coef_)!=1):
                imp = best_model.coef_
            if ("RandomForest" in name or "XGB" in name): 
                imp = best_model.feature_importances_
            feat_imp_result_series = pd.Series({'strategy': STRATEGY, 'test_len': test_len, 'model': name, 'metric': score, 'imp': imp})
            df_feat_imp = pd.concat([df_feat_imp, feat_imp_result_series.to_frame().T], ignore_index=True)
            #with open(f"{test_len}_cv_feature_importance.txt", 'a') as f:
            #    f.write(f'{name} {score}: {imp}\n')
            print("Feature importance::", imp)
            #FEATURES = x_train.columns
            indices = np.argsort(imp)
            plt.title(f'Feature Importances for {name} {score} test length {test_len}')
            plt.barh(range(len(indices)), imp[indices], color='b', align='center')
            plt.yticks(range(len(indices)), [FEATURES[i] for i in indices])
            plt.show()
        plt.boxplot(results, labels=names)
        plt.title(f'Algorithm Comparison for score: {score} and test length: {test_len}')
        plt.show()
    cv_output_path = f"{COMPANY}//results//{COMPANY}_cv_results.csv"
    df_cv_results.to_csv(cv_output_path, mode='a', header=not os.path.exists(cv_output_path))
    feat_output_path = f"{COMPANY}//results//{COMPANY}_feature_imp.csv"
    df_feat_imp.to_csv(feat_output_path, mode='a', header=not os.path.exists(feat_output_path))
    return df
        
                
evaluation_results = evaluate(best_models, test_len, tscv, X_train_sc, y_train)
